    "body": "I'm not sure I get the issue. Why can't we do a `<label>Sort by: <div id=\"index-selector\"></div></label>`?\n\nAnyway, we do not have to be Bootstrap compliant (at least, not for v1.0.0). If we really need to have the select outside of the label, I would simply allow passing a `selectId` option to the widget, and let the user correctly set the same `for` on the label.\n",
