    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@olance about your proposition yes it would work but it would be cool if we could find a simpler way to do it because it look like a lot of code for a simple `<label>`\n\nI would want to be able as a user to say `{label: 'select smg' }` in the option of the sort by selector.\n\nIf anyone has an idea on how to do it without breaking things for people that would be cool\n\nThe original request from @Shipow makes sense as a user perspective:\n\n> I think that adding a label should be allowed by the widget same way as refinementList allows header.\n",
