    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hmmm yes, it's simpler though limited. Unless we have a template option to which the `label` option value is passed so that it can be placed at any other place than the default one without having to create a custom widget just for that.\n\nOr \"as a user, I would like to be able to choose the label's place without having to create a whole new widget for it\" ^^\n",
